    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>26 November to 3 December 2020</td>
      <td>Project Proposal Forms reviewed by Havana-London Programme Board at the British Embassy in Havana</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>4 December 2020</td>
      <td>Outcome of full bids notified to implementers/bidders</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

